subSubSection.paragraph:
Colour. Naked areas of test golden yellow. Brown ambulacra bordered by single rows of brilliant, iridescent blue spots. The inflated anal cone is bluish white, with a brown peripheral ring and a dark brown anus. The spines are banded in reddish brown and yellowish white (
Hendler et al. 1995
). Juvenile can be pink-reddish with green spines banded by red stripes ( Humann & Deloach 2002 ).
